com.karusmc.xmc.commands

Class HelpCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.command.Command
      • com.karusmc.xmc.core.XMCommand
        • com.karusmc.xmc.commands.HelpCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandMapObserver, org.bukkit.command.PluginIdentifiableCommand

    public class HelpCommand
extends XMCommand
implements CommandMapObserver
    Default implementation of a help command. This class searches and returns all command usages within the owning plug-in. It implements the Observer interface and can be registered to a CommandMapProxy instance to be automatically updated whenever a new command instance is registered to it. Command hierarchy stored internally is flatten to optimize look-up performance.
    Author:
    PanteLegacy @ karusmc.com
